Message.En:
In the Dowe Valley, the dangerous presence
is undoubtedly <LQEM>.
Not long ago, that fearsome shadow was spotted
just across from the village.
If left alone, it's hard to predict the outcome.
If you're skilled, please defeat <LQVA> of them
to help resolve the situation.
Message.Jp:
ダウ渓谷で危険な存在といえば、やはり<LQEM>だろう。少し前も、あの恐ろしい影が村からすぐの対岸で確認されたばかりだ
放っておけばどういう結果を招くか解らない。もし腕に覚えがあるなら<LQVA>体倒し、事態の収束を図ってくれ
